<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-39-0244 </DOCNO><TEXT>By using the hyperelliptic formalism we obtain an explicit integral formulafor the four-massless-particle scattering amplitude at two loops in heteroticstring theory. We verify the main properties and in particular its finiteness.The corresponding expression for type II superstrings is also given.</TEXT></DOC>